Package com.briansanchez.blackjack

Class LoggingSingleton

java.lang.Object
java.util.logging.Logger
com.briansanchez.blackjack.LoggingSingleton
public class LoggingSingleton
extends Logger
This class implements a singleton design pattern in which the getLogger() method returns a fully configured instance. Classes should use this rather than creating their own Logger instance.
Author:
Brian Sanchez
